using the neutrinos directly

00:04:14.548 --> 00:04:16.089
you are studying
physics which is not

00:04:16.089 --> 00:04:19.769
described in the standard
theory, the standard model.

00:04:19.769 --> 00:04:21.680
So you have a path
there that you can now

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:24.920
articulate where you can
start small and grow big.

00:04:24.920 --> 00:04:27.154
So that's an extra piece.

