because it's so heavy

00:09:20.160 --> 00:09:22.280
it decays into all
sorts of things.

00:09:22.280 --> 00:09:26.304
So you cannot do the neutrino
science with it because it

00:09:26.304 --> 00:09:27.470
decays into too many things.

00:09:27.470 --> 00:09:30.650
So you don't get the
clean [INAUDIBLE] beam

00:09:30.650 --> 00:09:33.950
