00:15:58.360 --> 00:16:00.661
Either you improve the
performance by an upgrade,

00:16:00.661 --> 00:16:02.410
like the high luminosity
LHC, it gives you

00:16:02.410 --> 00:16:05.280
a factor of 10 in the
data rate so that you

00:16:05.280 --> 00:16:07.640
